        "Honours": "FerencvárosNemzeti Bajnokság I: 2015–16, 2018–19, 2019–20, 2020–21, 2021–22, 2022–23Hungarian Cup: 2014–15, 2015–16, 2016–17, 2021–22Hungarian League Cup: 2014–15Szuperkupa: 2015PécsNemzeti Bajnokság II: 2010–11",
